answersResultList.title: You are rarely annoying.
answersResultList.resultContent: You try, but you know what? You're human. Consideration for other people's wishes is always a good idea, but you can't always tiptoe around, and anyway, you have business to take care of. If you offend someone or harsh their mellow, you apologize and try to make it right. Being a good neighbor and citizen counts for something, doesn't it?
